				"description": {
					"value": "<p>10 feet. @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-ability-glossary-srd.v61oEQaDdcRpaZ9X]{Aura}</p><hr /><p>An Udug is surrounded by a veil of shadow that works as for the Darkness spell. While in direct sunlight or when they absorb magical light, an Udug gains the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.nlCjDvLMf2EkV2dl]{Quickened} condition until the end of their next turn that they can use only to [[/act stride]], [[/act step]] or Strike. If the Udug has the quickened condition for at least three consecutive turns, Light Eater is supressed for 24h. While Light Eater is supressed, if an Udug is in direct sunlight or magical light, they are considered @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} as long as they're under the light</p>",
